              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Habilidad Definitiva</span></p><p>Inflige 2 pts. de <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Daño Hydro</span> y <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepara la habilidad</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Inyección de amor</span>.</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/12/13/73555894/a1de05371a7005528534f295beec990c_5286757447019878216.png",
